<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title or metadata.title }}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description or metadata.description }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/bootstrap.min.css' | url }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/index.css' | url }}">
    <link rel="alternate" href="{{ metadata.feed.path | url }}" type="application/atom+xml" title="{{ metadata.title }}">
    <link rel="alternate" href="{{ metadata.jsonfeed.path | url }}" type="application/json" title="{{ metadata.title }}">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="{{ '/' | url }}"><img src="/img/logo.jpg" /></a>

      {#- Read more about `eleventy-navigation` at https://www.11ty.dev/docs/plugins/navigation/ #}
      <ul class="nav">
      {%- for entry in collections.all | eleventyNavigation %}
        <li class="nav-item{% if entry.url == page.url %} nav-item-active{% endif %}"><a href="{{ entry.url | url }}">{{ entry.title }}</a></li>
      {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </header>

    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img src="/img/madness1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
           <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Madness' most iconic</h5>
              <p>Madness classic photo</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="/img/madness2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Five reasons to be cheerful</h5>
              <p>Wow - Hands out</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="/img/madness3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>One step beyond</h5>
              <p>One step beyond</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="/img/madness4.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Madness are still nutty</h5>
              <p>Classic nutty</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"  data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"  data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>



    <main{% if templateClass %} class="{{ templateClass }}"{% endif %}>
      <h2>Update site 16/03 !!!</h2>
      {{ content | safe }}
    </main>
    <aside>
    <!-- width="100%" height="300" -->
      <div class="iframeContainer">
        <iframe title="deezer-widget" src="https://widget.deezer.com/widget/dark/track/143052958"  frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
      </div>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed sit amet fermentum elit. Pellentesque finibus accumsan suscipit. Mauris accumsan sit amet quam fermentum malesuada. Mauris bibendum laoreet urna, quis maximus nunc rhoncus vel. In in volutpat purus, vitae pretium ante. Curabitur vel magna accumsan, interdum metus sit amet, consequat metus. Curabitur sem elit, malesuada volutpat magna vitae, laoreet mattis elit.</p>
    </aside>
    <footer></footer>
    <script src="{{ '/js/bootstrap.min.js' | url }}"></script>
    <!-- Current page: {{ page.url | url }} 2049 -->
  </body>
</html>
